data.description: Welcome to this charming duplex located in the highly sought-after Highland Park Historic District. Situated on a spacious rare double lot of nearly 20,000 square feet, this Craftsman-style, 2-story duplex offers endless possibilities for a restoration or an expansion into a completely new development project. With a total of 2,118 square feet of living space, each unit within the duplex features a flexible floor plan that can accommodate either 2 or 3 bedrooms, allowing you to customize the layout to your preferences. One of the standout features of this property is the abundance of off-street parking, providing convenience for both residents and guests.  This property also boasts beautiful lush views overlooking tree tops in the neighborhood from observation decks. Unit 5924 and 5926 are both currently occupied, generating a rental income of $5250 per month. Property may be under the City of Los Angeles Rent Stabilization Ordinance.  Buyer to investigate and satisfy themselves as to any restrictions that may apply. Please do not disturb occupants. Showings 24-48 hrs notice during business hours only.  Buyer to conduct all necessary investigations. Buyer agrees to cooperate in a 1031 exchange.
